100
00:09:41,415 --> 00:09:43,084
Shit, Thelma.

101
00:09:43,167 --> 00:09:46,212
Why... He's gon' kill you!

102
00:09:46,295 --> 00:09:48,714
Well, he'd never let me go.

103
00:09:48,798 --> 00:09:52,260
