that's any fun.

104
00:09:52,343 --> 00:09:55,221
All he wants me to do is
hang around the house the whole time

105
00:09:55,304 --> 00:09:57,014
while he's out doing God only knows what.

106
00:09:58,015 --> 00:09:59,892
Well, you get what you settle for.

107
00:10:01,102 --> 00:10:04,063
I left him a note.

108
00:10:04,146 --> 00:10:07,566
I left him stuff to microwave.

109
00:10:31,048 --> 00:10:32,591
- Thelma.
- What?

110
00:10:54,780 --> 00:10:57,158
- Thelma, what are you doin'?
- Smoking.

111
00:11:00,286 --> 00:11:02,163
Hey. I'm Louise.

112
00:11:08,586 --> 00:11:11,964
I'll never make it.
Can't we just stop somewhere for a minute?

113
00:11:12,048 --> 00:11:15,134
Thelma, we're not gonna get to the cabin
till after dark as it is.

114
00:11:15,217 --> 00:11:17,595
Then what difference would it make
if we stopped?

115
00:11:17,678 --> 00:11:20,181
Come on.
I never get to do stuff like this.

116
00:11:20,264 --> 00:11:23,642
