- Fine. Okay.

117
00:12:02,306 --> 00:12:04,642
I haven't seen a place like this
since I left Texas.

118
00:12:04,725 --> 00:12:05,976
Isn't this fun?

119
00:12:19,490 --> 00:12:22,118
- Y'all want a drink?
- No, thanks.

120
00:12:22,201 --> 00:12:25,287
