and a Coke back, please.

121
00:12:25,371 --> 00:12:26,872
Thelma!

122
00:12:26,956 --> 00:12:29,917
Oh, what? Tell me something.
Is this my vacation or isn't it?

123
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:32,586
