131
00:12:52,898 --> 00:12:57,445
I'm gonna have a margarita
and a shot of Cuervo on the side.

132
00:12:58,112 --> 00:12:59,655
- Okay.
- All right! Get me another one.

133
00:13:03,325 --> 00:13:04,910
Hey.

134
