or I will never forgive you.

152
00:14:06,222 --> 00:14:08,015
Sure, that'd be fun.

153
00:14:11,644 --> 00:14:13,979
Geez, Louise. That wasn't very nice.

154
00:14:14,063 --> 00:14:16,190
Can't you tell
when somebody's hittin' on you?

155
00:14:16,273 --> 00:14:18,442
Oh, so what if he was?

156
00:14:18,526 --> 00:14:22,363
It's all your years of waiting tables
that's made you jaded, that's all.

157
00:14:22,446 --> 00:14:23,447
Maybe.

158
00:14:23,531 --> 00:14:25,449
Well, just relax, will you?

159
00:14:25,533 --> 00:14:27,826
- You're making me nervous.
- All right!

160
00:14:44,134 --> 00:14:47,096
<i>I woke up in a hotel,
I didn't know what to do</i>

161
