163
00:14:51,141 --> 00:14:53,769
<i>The news was talkin' 'bout a dragnet
up on the interstate</i>

164
00:14:55,479 --> 00:14:58,357
<i>Seems they were looking for a Cadillac
with Tennessee plates...</i>

165
00:14:58,440 --> 00:15:01,819
- Wonder if Darryl's home yet.
- Wonder if Jimmy's got back.

166
00:15:01,902 --> 00:15:04,071
Why don't you just tell him to get lost
once and for all?

167
00:15:04,154 --> 00:15:06,407
