that no-good husband of yours?

168
00:15:08,951 --> 00:15:10,869
This one's on Harlan.

169
00:15:12,871 --> 00:15:14,039
Thanks.

170
00:15:16,208 --> 00:15:17,876
Well, look.

171
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:20,212
Jimmy will come in off the road
and you won't be there.

172
00:15:20,296 --> 00:15:23,215
