when she was 17...</i>

194
00:16:43,796 --> 00:16:45,631
You got some great moves, honey.

195
00:16:46,465 --> 00:16:50,135
<i>Anyway, he wouldn't care,
hell, he gave them to his friends...</i>

196
00:16:53,013 --> 00:16:55,641
All right! Here we go!
Here we go! Here we go!

197
