200
00:17:12,408 --> 00:17:15,035
<i>Lord, I'm crazy about a Mercury</i>

201
00:17:16,036 --> 00:17:21,917
<i>I'm gonna buy me a Mercury
and cruise it on down the road</i>

202
00:18:03,959 --> 00:18:05,753
Hey, hey! Thelma!

203
00:18:05,836 --> 00:18:08,172
- Oh, Louise.
