little lady.

216
00:19:03,519 --> 00:19:04,895
Look, have you seen my friend?

217
00:19:04,978 --> 00:19:07,439
Your friend? Yeah. Yeah.

218
00:19:07,523 --> 00:19:09,566
She was out there dancing.
Dancing.

219
00:19:12,945 --> 00:19:15,280
How you feeling now, darling?

220
00:19:15,364 --> 00:19:16,615
Oh, thanks.

221
00:19:17,783 --> 00:19:19,785
I think I'm starting
to feel a little better.

222
00:19:20,744 --> 00:19:22,704
