to me too.

223
00:19:22,788 --> 00:19:24,373
- Hey.
- You know that?

224
00:19:24,456 --> 00:19:26,291
I think I need to keep walking.

225
00:19:26,375 --> 00:19:28,961
Wait a minute. Wait a minute.
Wait a minute.

226
00:19:29,044 --> 00:19:31,463
