- What?

229
00:19:35,634 --> 00:19:37,553
Hey, quit it. Stop it. Stop it. Stop.

230
00:19:37,636 --> 00:19:40,264
Thelma, Thelma, listen to me.
Listen to me.

231
00:19:40,347 --> 00:19:44,142
